Original SCM and entailed distribution

set.seed(1)

X3 <- runif(100)
X1 <- 2 * X3 + rnorm(100)
X2 <- (0.5 * X1)^2 + rnorm(100)^2
X4 <- X2 + 2*sin(X3 + rnorm(100))

plot(y=X4, x=X3)
